H0.text: Ovaries are the organs considered the female gonads.

H1.text: Testes are the organs considered the female gonads.

H2.text: Uterus is considered a female gonad.

H3.text: Fallopian tubes are the organs considered the female gonads.

A4.text: The ovary is a gonad in the female reproductive system that produces ova.

A5.text: He thought the ovaries produced female seeds, and the testicles produced male seeds.
